 press for a maiden World Cup appearance and temporarily shelved herTeam GBambitions.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a coveted full-time contract\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"offer\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 787}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15s game\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 803}, {\"ngram\": \"Kildunne\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"a maiden World Cup appearance\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"herTeam GBambitions\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were a lot of tears and a lot of guilt and heartbreak in that moment,\\\" she admitted.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 926}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"guilt\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 984}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the biggest heartbreak I have ever had in my life and the hardest decision I have ever had to make as well but I do not regret it.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1139, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest heartbreak\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1031}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the hardest decision\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think everything happens for a reason and so I refocused on going to the World Cup.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"a reason\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were always more Olympics to come and so from then it just became an itch I could not scratch.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more Olympics\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"an itch\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was never going to let that go and I was never going to be told that I could not do that again.\\\"\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Yorkshire native has now been chosen as part of Team GB's12-strong sevens squadfor this summer's Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\", \"score\": 0.9995742388884259, \"rank\": 0.0004239947812319426, \"text\": \"Yorkshire\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yorkshire_County_Cricket_Club\"}, {\"begin\": 1539, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997987743, \"rank\": 2.0121473391619391e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1477}, {\"ngram\": \"this summer's Games\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kildunne, labelled the 'best player in the world' by Ugo Monye, was named 2024 Women's Six Nations Player of the Championshipafter a staggering nine triesin five matches.\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Monye\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ugo Monye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Monye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ugo_Monye\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kildunne\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'best player\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the Championshipafter\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1677}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics has always pulled on her heartstrings - as a schoolgirl, she wrote a 6,000-word English assignment on Dame Jessica Ennis-Hill.\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"score\": 0.7309220753296087, \"rank\": 0.3641753581953467, \"text\": \"Dame\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Knight\"}, {\"begin\": 1839, \"end\": 1857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"her heartstrings\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"a schoolgirl\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1787}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6,000-word English assignment\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was a simple self-shot video from Team GB's first-ever women'srugby sevenssquad that cemented her ambition.\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1901, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999852347184, \"rank\": 1.4764986328454254e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a simple self-shot video\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1895}, {\"ngram\": \"her ambition\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Of course, I watched the Olympics growing up as everyone else does,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2055, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I remember when at Rio 2016 when the rugby sevens was first announced as a sport, I found a video on YouTube that was the girls getting kitted out before Rio.\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 0.9999999999956799, \"rank\": 4.428531979091993e-12, \"text\": \"YouTube\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}, {\"begin\": 2215, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999987054085717, \"rank\": 1.2945931660227403e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"the rugby\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"a video\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2158}, {\"ngram\": \"the girls\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I watched that video every single day because it felt like I was there with them.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that video\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sure the Games are cool, but seeing the life outside of it really inspired another side of me.\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"the life\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"another side\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that really inspired the creative side of me as well, seeing life at a new angle.\\\"\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the creative side\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2472}, {\"ngram\": \"a new angle\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kildunne herself is an incredibly creative person on and off the rugby pitch.\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kildunne\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredibly creative person\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"the rugby pitch\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2567}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Extracting pleasure in the simplicity of just taking a picture on her camera, Kildunne admits amateur photography is the only hobby which allows her to truly switch off from sport.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the simplicity\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"a picture\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"her camera\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2645}, {\"ngram\": \"Kildunne\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"amateur photography\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"the only hobby\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2700}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Team GB's rugby sevens' self-appointed official photographer, Kildunne will look to capture her summer in Paris from every angle.\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2754, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.999999852347184, \"rank\": 1.4764986328454254e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2860, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997987743, \"rank\": 2.0121473391619391e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"self-appointed official photographer\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"Kildunne\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"her summer\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"every angle\", \"from\": 2871, \"to\": 2882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People speak about switching on and switching off but I can not switch off until I have that camera in my hand,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2885, \"to\": 3008, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2892}, {\"ngram\": \"that camera\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2985}, {\"ngram\": \"my hand\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 2996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My brain always goes a million miles an hour and I will be thinking about a pass that I made or a gap that I saw that we did not quite get.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My brain\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"a million miles\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"a pass\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"a gap\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have found this recipe that works so well for me where my brain stops and goes off being an Ellie Kildunne rugby cap and to a girl with a camera in her hands.\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3246, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Kildunne\", \"score\": 0.9999933284547928, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellie Kildunne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Kildunne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Kildunne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this recipe\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3176}, {\"ngram\": \"my brain\", \